Apify-derived capability records are marked with `provenance: apify` and a
per-record `source` field pointing back to the upstream dataset. The mapping
from Apify's capability-presence schema to canimcp's per-sub-feature taxonomy
is conservative: only directly-attested capabilities are recorded; everything
else is left `unknown`.

